	</div>
	<div data-role="content">
	  <p>The school is consistently ranked highly in leading surveys of higher education. The emphasis is always on the practical application of skills and knowledge and students from our programmes have an excellent record for employment once they graduate.</p>
	  <p><strong>Get a degree that counts</strong> - Think about studying in one of our<em> undergraduate programmes</em> in Management, IT, Computing and Tourism</p>
	  <p><strong>Enhance your career - </strong>Choose from one of our 9 specialist <em>MBA programmes</em>, or other masters programmes
