	  <ul>
	    <li>Carmarthen</li>
	    <li>Jobs Well</li>
      </ul>
	  <p><strong>Career Opportunities</strong></p>
	  <ul>
	    <li>This degree can lead to a wide range of career opportunities as a freelance artist/designer; employed artist/designer; art administrator; or community art worker etc. This course may also provide an ideal platform to become either a secondary or primary school teacher or an art therapist following additional speColeg Sir Gart training. It could also be the basis for other postgraduate study.</li>
      </ul>
	  <p><strong>Key Features</strong>    </p>
